title: Nee Varuvai Ena
subTitle: Ganesh falls for his extremely caring and helpful new neighbour, Nandini, who lives in a house opposite to his. But, when Ganesh and his parents put forth a marriage proposal, she turns them down.

title: Aalavandhan
subTitle: Nandu and Vijay, brothers with a traumatic past, struggle with memories of abuse. Driven by his delusions, Nandu plans to kill Vijay's fiancee, mistaking her for his abusive stepmother.

title: Dhill
subTitle: Kanagavel, an aspiring police officer, beats up a man for misbehaving with his girlfriend. That man turns out to be a corrupt police officer who later starts harassing Kanagavel and his family.

title: Alaipayuthey
subTitle: After eloping and getting married to each other by going against their families, a couple realises that living in a marriage is not as simple as it seems.

subTitle: Prabhu, from a poor family, lies to Sukanya about his wealth before their wedding. Her mother, disapproving, plots to destroy their marriage.
